@startuml heterogeneity_matrix
!theme plain
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam defaultFontName "Segoe UI"
skinparam defaultFontSize 11
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam roundCorner 8

title **Agent Heterogeneity — Multi-Model, Multi-Provider Architecture**

skinparam object {
  BackgroundColor #FAFAFA
  BorderColor #BDBDBD
  FontColor #1A1A1A
}

object "**Engagement Manager**" as em #E3F2FD {
  Model = Claude Haiku (Small)
  Provider = Anthropic
  Tools = read_client_request()
  Output = Analysis Plan JSON
  Role = Task decomposition
  Reasoning = Fast, structured task
}

object "**Market Researcher**" as mr #E8F5E9 {
  Model = Claude Sonnet (Medium)
  Provider = Anthropic
  Tools = search_web(), read_document(), summarize_source()
  Output = Market Analysis JSON
  Role = Market investigation
  Reasoning = Good synthesis ability
}

object "**Financial Analyst**" as fa #FFF3E0 {
  Model = GPT-4o-mini (Medium)
  Provider = OpenAI
  Tools = calculate(), create_projection(), query_data(), create_chart()
  Output = Financial Analysis JSON
  Role = Quantitative analysis
  Reasoning = Strong numerical reasoning
}

object "**Risk Analyst**" as ra #FFEBEE {
  Model = Mistral Medium
  Provider = Mistral
  Tools = search_web(), read_document(), assess_risk()
  Output = Risk Matrix JSON
  Role = Risk identification
  Reasoning = Edge case thinking
}

object "**Strategy Consultant**" as sc #F3E5F5 {
  Model = Claude Opus / GPT-4 (Large)
  Provider = Anthropic / OpenAI
  Tools = read_market_research(), read_financial_analysis(), read_risk_assessment()
  Output = Consulting Report JSON
  Role = Synthesis & recommendation
  Reasoning = Best writing & reasoning
}

object "**Evaluator**" as ev #FFFDE7 {
  Model = Claude Sonnet (Large)
  Provider = Anthropic
  Tools = read_final_report(), score_report()
  Output = Scorecard JSON
  Role = Independent quality judge
  Reasoning = Critical assessment
}

em -[hidden]right- mr
mr -[hidden]right- fa
fa -[hidden]down- ra
ra -[hidden]left- sc
sc -[hidden]left- ev

note as N1
  **Heterogeneity Dimensions:**
  1. **Model Size:** Small → Medium → Large
  2. **Provider:** Anthropic, OpenAI, Mistral
  3. **Tools:** Different tool sets per agent
  4. **Output Schema:** Different JSON structures
  5. **Reasoning Style:** Structured vs. analytical vs. creative
end note

@enduml
